title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 105: Anew
description: The LP is back again with a new world. With all the changes to the Minecraft game lately, and me starting anew... it had me thinking about the past and how this game used to be.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 106: Glowing Tree
description:
Today we check out some of the tunnels surrounding our home. These tunnels are all potential future building locations.

We place the mark for our new home and territory. We also play around a bit with a few ways we can utilize lighting in a cool way.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 107: Cave Spiders
description:
Sorry for having another long delay in the LP series. Things should be back to normal schedule now.

Today we experiment a bit with mob behavior, fishing rods, talk about base plans, and check out the nearby, cave spider infested, abandoned mine shaft.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 108: A Strange Farm
description: Today we start building a strange passive mob farm and a wheat farm, together as one... in beautiful harmony. This was made possible thanks to a great tip I received from "AstroGnomical" about how farmland cannot be trampled if there is a fence under it.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 109: Area 51
description: We work on the strange farm again. It gets even stranger today. I wasn't expecting it to take this long, but I guess it is actually a fairly big project.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 110: Bleeding Ears
description:
Todays episode is mostly dedicated to working on our wheat/cow farm again. The UFO gets nearly finished and the lower farm potion gets polished up a bit too.

The main thing left to do is build a holding / killing chamber for the animals and connect together the lower and upper portions of the farm.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 111: Spawners & Stuff
description:
Lots of random things today. Cows, wheat, slimes, monster spawners, reeds, enchanting... you name, this episode has it all!

This is what I use to locate slime chunks:
http://mcslimes.appspot.com/

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 112: Corruption
description:
Well this is a first for me. I've had worlds get messed up from patches or get chunk errors... but never completely fail before. I'm guessing something got stuck in an infinite loop, causing the the frame rate to drop to like 1 frame every 5 to 10 seconds.

So basically I have reverted back to where we were at Episode #109. Not to worry though, I am quickly recovering from the loss.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 113: Boats & Carts
description:
Today we mess around with boat and mine cart ideas for the cave. Let me know what you think of the ideas. The water seems more intrusive than I was expecting, now that I see a visual example of it.

Sorry for the short episode, and somewhat lack of episodes recently. I've been busy trying to get lots of construction work done before winter comes.

(ShoutOuts)
docm77: http://www.youtube.com/user/docm77

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 114: Spider Overload
description:
My plan for a quick starter project ends up stealing the show. I was actually really shocked just how effective this ended up being. The spawning rates are pretty insane.

This type of trap will get you lots of string (can be made to wool), spider eyes, and most important... XP.

title: Etho Plays Minecraft - Episode 115: Cheap Suit
description:
I feel spoiled now. Little by little I keep getting nicer things for myself in our new world. I still really miss the TNT though...

Many thanks to all that have donated to help me continue making new videos. Generally, I spend the money on computer improvements to make video production easier.

Jonathan (Bunglist) suggested I get the Logitech G700 wireless mouse.

description:

This thing is great for gaining xp levels for enchanting, but it also a great source of wool and spider eyes. I've already got over 10 stacks of wool saved up just from testing the spider systems built so far.
